title: 255: Takeaways from Wild Card Weekend
itunes:title: 255: Takeaways from Wild Card Weekend
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks break down the biggest moments from the first round of the playoffs. Are the Falcons and their high-flying offense set to make another run (7:02)? Can the Jaguars defense carry them to the Super Bowl (11:25)? We have you covered throughout the NFL Playoffs and into draft season here on Move the Sticks presented by the Ford F-Series.
